data.title: Philippine Free TV Station GMA Announces 2016 Anime Line-Up
data.meta_description: Philippine free TV station, GMA revealed its 2016 anime line-up.
data.text:
Philippine free TV station GMA revealed its 2016 anime line-up under their "GMA Astig Authority" banner in a recent TV ad.

The TV ad revealed the following shows that will get reruns next year. These shows are: Voltes V, Daimos, Sonic X, Virtua Fighter, and Magic Knight Rayearth though it is mislabeled under the "new shows" category. Rayearth aired in the said TV station during the early 2000's every weekends.

The TV ad also revealed that new seasons of Hayate the Combat Butler, Pokemon XY, Doraemon, and Bleach will also air next year, with Bleach airing its final season. Finally, the following shows will make their premiere next year. These shows are: Bakugan: Mechatnium Stage, Dragon Collection, Oreca Battle, and Yo-Kai Watch.
